Liner Notes ::
Cities Sampler Volume 11 is a compilation of performances recorded live in the Cities 97 studios that cannot be found anywhere else. One hundred percent of the proceeds from the Cities Sampler benefit Minnesota charities. Cities 97 has raised nearly two million dollars and has contributed to programs like "Cities Kids" - a partnership with the Community University Health Center that brings health and wellness care to children in need in the Twin Cities - and many others. Thank you for making this unique CD such a huge success!
